returns._0: liquidToken Address of the token received from the deployment strategy.
returns._1: liquidTokenAmount Amount of the liquid token received.

params.account_: Address of the account on behalf of which the tokens are deposited.

returns._0: sharesAmount Amount of shares issued for the deposited assets.
token Address of the token received from the harvest.
returns._1: tokenAmount Amount of the token received.

params.masterTokenAddress_: The address of the lys token
params.ownerAddress_: The address of the owner of the vault
params.sharesName_: The name for the shares issued by the vault
params.sharesSymbol_: The symbol for the shares issued by the vault
params.underlyingTokenAddress_: The address of the underlying token for the vault
params.vaultsRegistryAddress_: The address of the registry where vaults are managed

params.account_: Address of the account receiving the assets.
params.caller_: Address representing the master token invoking the redemption.

returns._0: assetsAmount Amount of assets received for the redeemed shares.

params.account_: Address of the account from which shares are burned.
params.caller_: Address representing the master token invoking the withdrawal.

returns._0: sharesAmount Amount of shares burned to perform the withdrawal.

deployAssets().notice: Deploys assets according to the defined strategy for asset management.

deposit(uint256,address).notice: Allows assets to be deposited in exchange for shares, adhering to access controls.

harvest().notice: Harvests earnings from the strategy, adhering to access controls.

redeem(uint256,address,address).notice: Redeems shares for underlying assets, adhering to access controls.

withdraw(uint256,address,address).notice: Allows the withdrawal of assets in exchange for burning shares, adhering to access controls.
